{
  "stem": "23737.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I suppose we survived because we were so many in the truck that we warmed each other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as we were taken from our home, we took a blanket with us so there was a blanket to lie on and things like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was absolutely freezing conditions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can imagine in December Hungary is not-- and that part of Europe is very cold in December.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't pleasant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived in Belsen, we didn't know what kind of a place this is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were taken to our camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we went in, we had no German guards at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We only had Hungarian guards and mostly our own people who were our guards.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a lageralteste.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's how they called the main leader of the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I became very, very friendly with him eventually.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he helped as much as he could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we got there, the barracks were all two and three-story beds in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was with a girl whom I knew from Budapest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she says, she went-- as she was walking down one of the aisles, she says, come here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm want to show you something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she says, look at that inscription on that bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was an inscription of her sister's.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was here from that date to that date and taken to Switzerland on such and such a date.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She was taken to Switzerland at the beginning-- the first week of December.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I can't remember the date anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the story of it is that after the German occupation of Hungary, there were an awful lot of people who paid-- who had money.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
